sentences: Irène Schweizer (born 2 June 1941) is a Swiss jazz and free improvising pianist.
She was born in Schaffhausen, Switzerland.
With Yusef Lateef, Uli Trepte and Mani Neumeier, she performed at the Montreux Jazz Festival in 1967.
